
This is version of Mandelbrot for CP/M
Code should work on any Z80 hardware.

Tested on
* RC2014 clone (7.3MHz and 20MHz system clock, 115200 baud terminal)
* Udo Munk Z80pack CP/M cpmsim (8MHz and 20MHz) with same results

Code compiled using pasmo assembler.
(fidedpt.asm, mandelbrot.asm required patching)

